This code checks the advisory content and route/time to determine if an alert should be sent. It ignores alerts for non-Avellino-Fisciano routes, weekend days before 8AM, and after 6PM on Friday. For other valid days from Monday to Thursday (inclusive) between 8AM and 6PM, it sends the alert message.

