const advisoryContent = NjTransit.newBusAdvisory.AdvisoryContent;
if (!advisoryContent) {
  Sms.sendMeText.setMessage('New bus advisory without content');
} else {
  const lowerCaseContent = advisoryContent.toLowerCase();
  if (lowerCaseContent.includes('line indicated') && lowerCaseContent.includes('crisis hours')) {
    // Assuming 'crisis hours' is a keyword indicating pendulum time in NJ
    Sms.sendMeText.setMessage(`New bus advisory: ${NjTransit.newBusAdvisory.RouteAndTime} - Link: ${NjTransit.newBusAdvisory.Link}`);
  } else {
    // Scarta l'avviso se non cade negli orari di pendolarismo in un giorno feriale
    Sms.sendMeText.setMessage('');
  }
}
```
This code assumes that 'crisis hours' is a keyword indicating the bus advisory falls within pendulum time in NJ, and only sends an SMS if this condition is met. Otherwise, it does not send any message (scarta l'avviso). The accessor `NjTransit.newBusAdvisory.RouteAndTime` includes the route and time information of the advisory.

