const route = 'X'; // Replace with actual route name
const hour = Meta.currentUserTime.hour();
// Define alert hours as 7am to 9am, 12pm to 2pm, and 5pm to 6pm
const isAlertHour = (hour >= 7 && hour < 10) || (hour >= 12 && hour < 14) || (hour >= 17 && hour <= 18);
// Define weekdays as Monday to Friday inclusive
const isWeekday = Meta.currentUserTime.isoWeekday() >= 1 && Meta.currentUserTime.isoWeekday() <= 5;
if (!isAlertHour || !isWeekday) {
  Sms.sendMeText.setMessage('');
} else {
  const message = `New bus advisory for route ${route}: ${NjTransit.newBusAdvisory.RouteAndTime}`;
  Sms.sendMeText.setMessage(message);
}
```
This code checks if the current hour is within the alert hours (7am to 9am, 12pm to 2pm, and 5pm to 6pm) and if the day of week is a weekday (Monday to Friday). If either criterion fails, no SMS message is sent. Otherwise, an SMS message with the advisory information for route 'X' is sent.

